OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,FProsecutors are "providing early
OL,7,Finvestigative advice" to the police as
OL,8,Fthey carry out their inquiries into
OL,9,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor and Lord
OL,10,FPeter Mandelson's links to Jeffrey
OL,11,FEpstein, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,12,F(CPS) has said.
OL,14,FThe former prince and Lord Mandelson,
OL,15,Fwho was appointed as the UK's
OL,16,Fambassador to the US, were both
OL,17,Farrested last month on suspicion of
OL,18,Fmisconduct in public office over their
OL,19,Fconnections with the paedophile
OL,20,Ffinancier.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@UO]
