OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775135469
OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,FThey have since been released under
OL,7,Finvestigation.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, a spokesperson for the
OL,15,FCPS said: "We can confirm that we are
OL,16,Fnow providing early investigative
OL,17,Fadvice to the Metropolitan Police
OL,18,FService regarding the force's
OL,19,Finvestigation into a 72-year-old man
OL,20,Fand will continue to liaise as
OL,21,Frequested.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
