CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775135469
OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,F"We can now also confirm that we are
OL,7,Fproviding early investigative advice
OL,8,Fto Thames Valley Police in relation to
OL,9,Fa 66-year-old man.
OL,11,F"We remain ready to support any
OL,12,Finvestigation if needed."
OL,14,FAndrew's brother King Charles has
OL,15,Ffaced calls from the family of Epstein
OL,16,Fvictim Virginia Giuffre to meet with
OL,17,Fsurvivors during his state visit to
OL,18,Fthe US this month.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@YO]
