CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775135469
OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,FAddressing the calls, Prime Minister
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer said: "In relation to
OL,8,Fthe King, I think it's important to
OL,9,Fappreciate this is part of the 250
OL,10,F(year) celebrations (of American
OL,11,Findependence).
OL,13,F"It's a long-planned visit, and the US
OL,14,Fand UK are close allies, have been for
OL,15,Fa very, very long time."
OL,17,FITV News understands that the ongoing
OL,18,Fpolice investigation into the Mr
OL,19,FMountbatten-Windsor will prevent any
OL,20,Fsuch meeting from taking place.
OL,26,@oD@XOUrD@ApmrD@FpnrD@UpmsD@MpnuD@AOUwD@
