OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,7,F(NPCC) also announced on Tuesday that
OL,8,Fthe police response to the release of
OL,9,Fthe so-called Epstein files by the US
OL,10,FDepartment of Justice is to be
OL,11,F"stepped up".
OL,13,FA dedicated group will look at the
OL,14,F"scale, scope and nature of any
OL,15,Fpotential UK-based VAWG (violence
OL,16,Fagainst women and girls) offending
OL,17,Fwithin the files", the NPCC added.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]vD@AOUyD@QO]
