OL,3,CCPS giving 'investigative advice' to
OL,4,Cpolice in Epstein probe
OL,6,FIt has also invited alleged victims of
OL,7,FEpstein who have spoken to UK media to
OL,8,Ftalk to investigators about potential
OL,9,Fcrimes that may have taken place on
OL,10,FBritish soil.
OL,12,FIt was previously reported that nine
OL,13,Fpolice forces from across the UK are
OL,14,Fcarrying out assessments following the
OL,15,Frelease of more than 3.5 million
OL,16,Fdocuments linked to Jeffrey Epstein on
OL,17,FJanuary 30.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
